  "prompt": "What is the best alarm clock on the market?",
  "response": "Choosing the best alarm clock depends on individual preferences and needs, but here are a few highly regarded options as of 2023:\n\n1. **Philips Wake-Up Light Alarm Clock**:\n   - Features a sunrise simulation that gradually wakes you up with increasing light intensity.\n   - Includes natural sounds to help facilitate easy and gentle wake-ups.\n   - Has customizable brightness settings and FM radio.\n\n2. **iHome iBT29BG Bluetooth Color Changing Alarm Clock**:\n   - Offers Bluetooth connectivity for streaming music.\n   - Features a built-in speakerphone.\n   - Includes color-changing lights for a customizable wake-up experience.\n\n3. **Loftie Smart Alarm Clock**:\n   - Designed for a healthy sleep routine with no blue light emissions.\n   - Provides guided meditation and breathing exercises.\n   - Features white noise and nature sound options.\n\n4. **Sonic Bomb Dual Extra Loud Alarm Clock with Bed Shaker**:\n   - Best for heavy sleepers.\n   - Includes a vibrating bed shaker.\n   - Has an incredibly loud alarm sound.\n\n5. **Ruggie Alarm Clock**:\n   - Innovative design that requires you to get out of bed and step on the rug to turn off the alarm.\n   - Features motivational quotes and customizable settings.\n\n6. **Lenovo Smart Clock**:\n   - Compact and easy to use.\n   - Integrates with Google Assistant for smart home control.\n   - Allows streaming music, setting reminders, checking the weather, and more.\n\nWhen choosing an alarm clock, consider factors like alarm sound options, additional features (like FM radio or smart connectivity), design, ease of use, and how gentle or aggressive you prefer your wake-up experience to be.",
